sequenceDiagram
    participant S as Support UAV
    participant C as Fusion center
    participant T as Tracker history
    S->>S: Capture observation at c
    Note over C: Frames c to a-1 publish without message
    S->>C: Message arrives at a
    C->>T: Restore snapshot before c
    C->>T: Insert support at capture frame c
    C->>T: Replay c through a
    C->>C: Publish frame a online result
    Note over C: Earlier online outputs remain frozen
    C->>T: Final replay produces offline-corrected history
